Package ABSmodJ

Class Summary
Action This class is the super class to the two classes: ConditionalAction and ScheduledAction.
Activity Extend this class to implement activity constructs.
ActivitySuper Super class to all variations of activity classes: Activity, TrigActivity, ExtActivity, ExtTrigActivity.
AOSimulationModel This class is extended to create a simulation model using the Activity Object World View.
Behaviour Super class of all behaviour construct classes, including action constructs.
ConditionalAction Extend this class to implement conditional action constructs.
ExtActivity Extend this class to implement extended activity constructs.
ExtTrigActivity Extend this class to implement extended triggered activity constructs.
OutputSet Use this class to create objects that represent trajectory or sample sets.
SBNotice This class is used to create scheduled behaviour notices stored on the sbl (scheduled behaviour list).
ScheduledAction Extend this class to implement scheduled action constructs.
TriangularVariate This class allows the creation of Triangular Random Number Generator.
TrigActivity Extend this class to implement triggered activity constructs.
